  <prompt>Migrate remaining BFF call sites that go through `Spaarke.Core/Cache/DistributedCacheExtensions.cs` directly (using `CreateKey()` helper without `ITenantCache`). Goal: every BFF code path that touches the distributed cache does so via `ITenantCache`.</prompt>
  <role>Spaarke .NET developer.</role>
  <goal>Outside the wrapper itself + tests, BFF has ZERO direct `DistributedCacheExtensions.CreateKey` or `IDistributedCache.*` calls.</goal>
  <context><background>`Spaarke.Core/Cache/DistributedCacheExtensions.cs` remains as a shared helper (other consumers may still use it outside BFF). BFF moves to `ITenantCache` for tenant-scope enforcement.</background><relevant-files><file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/</file></relevant-files></context>
  <constraints><constraint source="spec">FR-06 atomic migration.</constraint></constraints>
